{"title":"题周恩来童年读书处　［外三首］","authors":["周克玉"],"dates":[{"year":2001,"month":1,"day":21}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"题周恩来童年读书处"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"［外三首］"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"周克玉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丰碑高耸记风雨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家塾遗景蕴根底。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昔日大鹏起飞处，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春潮又涌书声起。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无题"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灯下焦灰重重叠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"犹有飞翼纷纷来。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鸟为食亡寻常事，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人因财焚究可哀。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"题恒山悬空寺"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一寺飞挂翠屏峰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雕梁画栋悬壁空"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三教同堂人共识"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千年难解神奇功"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"题铁道游击队"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遥想当年飞车兵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千里铁道敌胆惊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"神出鬼没游击战"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纵横驰骋显威风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扎根泥土双脚稳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旗飘蓝天泾渭清"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"留得一支琵琶曲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长久响在人心中"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}